╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  HELIX TRAINER — Exercise 3.5: Case and Replace                 ║
║  Category: Changes               Difficulty: ★☆☆ Fundamental    ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

COMMANDS TO LEARN
─────────────────
  ~     Toggle case of selection
  `     Convert selection to lowercase
  Alt-` Convert selection to UPPERCASE
  r     Replace each character in selection with a given char

INSTRUCTIONS
────────────
  Part A: Convert the SHOUTING lines to lowercase.
  Part B: Convert the whispering lines to UPPERCASE.
  Part C: Replace the dashes with equals signs.

  For Part A: Select the text, press ` (backtick) for lowercase.
  For Part B: Select the text, press Alt-` for uppercase.
  For Part C: Select the dashes, press r then = .

────────────────────────── PRACTICE ──────────────────────────────

THIS IS TOO LOUD
PLEASE STOP SHOUTING
this is too quiet
make me louder please
--------------------

────────────────────────── EXPECTED ──────────────────────────────

this is too loud
please stop shouting
THIS IS TOO QUIET
MAKE ME LOUDER PLEASE
====================

──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
HINTS (read only if stuck):
  Hint 1: For "THIS IS TOO LOUD", press x to select the line,
          then ` (backtick) to convert to lowercase.
  Hint 2: For "this is too quiet", press x then Alt-` to
          convert to uppercase.
  Hint 3: For the dashes, press x to select, then r then = .
          r replaces every character in the selection with the
          character you type next.
